OL,3,CEngland's only Balalaika orchestra
OL,4,Cissues plea for new members
OL,6,FVideo report by Paul Crone
OL,8,FFor many, playing the recorder or
OL,9,Fclanging a triangle at school was a
OL,10,Fritual part of growing up, but one
OL,11,Fmusical group in Manchester is
OL,12,Foffering people a chance to play a
OL,13,Fmore unusual instrument - the
OL,14,FBalalaika.
OL,16,FThe Balalaika is a Russian string
OL,17,Finstrument, similar to a triangular
OL,18,Fguitar, but with only three strings.
