OL,3,CEngland's only Balalaika orchestra
OL,4,Cissues plea for new members
OL,6,FIt would mean members would have to
OL,7,Ftravel 500 miles to Paris to join the
OL,8,Fclosest Balalaika group.
OL,10,FBrian believes the instrument's
OL,11,FRussian heritage may be putting
OL,12,Fpotential members off. The group has
OL,13,Fonly a few bookings so far this year.
OL,15,FBalalaika lessons used to be offered
OL,16,Fin more than 10 schools in Manchester,
OL,17,Fnow there is only one.
